# Full XFCE desktop (skip if installing CachyOS XFCE edition — already provided).
# Select via fzf at bootstrap. xfce4/xfce4-goodies are pacman GROUPS, so pacman
# pulls all members; --needed in bootstrap skips already-installed ones.
xfce4
xfce4-goodies
# X11 server (xrdp+xorgxrdp need Xorg even if not used locally)
xorg-server
xorg-xinit
